descriptionHtml:
The AG SmartFarm App, the mobile app for AG Agras drones, Is now available!

The AG SmartFarm App offers diverse, practical functions such as data display, device management, field sharing and management, teamwork and measurement tools, to provide end-to-end service support for your spraying and spreading operations.

with the app, you can view clearer data on your Agras aircraft while controlling and managing your device with superior ease and efficiency.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Adds field labels to better organize and locate your fields
